            Islands in the Storm:
              date: '2018-05-14'
              text:
              - At long last, Corla is home. Almost. Due to the transient nature of inter‑reality movement, she is on an unfamiliar Tsarin island, somewhat <i>before</i> she left. Now she must find her way across Tsarein, while ensuring she does not affect her own past.
