      text:
      - Eons ago, I decided to write a novel. I then decided, as a language nerd, I should create a number of constructed languages, and now I’ve decided to put this on the web. So I’m two levels away from <em>actually</em> writing the thing. One day….
      - The <cite>Coelacanth Quartet</cite> details the adventures of Corla, a Tsarin telepath far from home.
      - This quartet comprises a cycle of four stories that can be enjoyed starting at any point.
